## Code Review: OpenWok — restaurant-onboarding_20260320
**Date:** 2026-03-20

### Verdict: FIX FIRST

Two issues block shipping: (1) TOCTOU security bug in menu item ownership verification — update happens BEFORE ownership check, so any authenticated user can modify any restaurant's menu items; (2) `make clippy` fails with 2 errors in frontend.

